<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA7">
<l>yāmē yaruviṉaiyōñ cēyō meṉṉeñciṉār</l>
<l>tāmē yaṇukkarāyc cārntoḻintār pūmēya</l>
<l>cemmātai niṉmārpil cērvittu pāriṭanta</l>
<l>vammā niṟpātat taruku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We, we of difficult Karma are far. Those of our heart,</l>
<l>being close they have stopped approaching. Father,</l>
<l>who dug up the earth, joining the flower-dwelling red lady to [your] chest,</l>
<l>I shall approach your feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
